description: The investment objective of the FT Vest Nasdaq-100 Buffer ETF - September (the "Fund") is to seek to provide investors with returns (before fees and expenses) that match the price return of the Invesco QQQ Trust SM, Series 1 (the "Underlying ETF"), up to a predetermined upside cap of 17.34% while providing a buffer (before fees and expenses) against the first 10% of Underlying ETF losses, over the period from September 23, 2024 through September 19, 2025.
name: FT Vest Nasdaq-100 Buffer ETF - September
